</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_305" id="151v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab facs="#facs_305_r2l1">Poppen vnd <expan>Pernharte<ex>n</ex></expan> von
                        adlecʒheim </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_305_r2l2">ʒu Adlecʒheim <expan>geſeſſ<ex>en</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_305_r2l3"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> ~ dıe von Adlecʒheim / vns ıſt / von ſıfrıde ſchenken <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> fürbracht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_305_r2l4"><expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan> . wıe Jn etlıch eẅr dıener nehſt <expan>gefang<ex>en</ex></expan> haben in dem namen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_305_r2l5">als ſıe <expan>meynte<ex>n</ex></expan> / 
<del rend="strikethrough">d </del> er ſölt ein <expan>vnrechfertıg<ex>er</ex></expan> man ſein . Tun wır eẅch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_305_r2l6">ʒu <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> . daʒ er etwıeuıl Jare <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ſchreıb<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> in <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> ſchreıb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_305_r2l7"><expan>ſtube<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>geweſ<ex>en</ex></expan> ıſt vnd vns <expan>fröm<ex>m</ex>klıch</expan> gedıent hat denn daʒ er von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_305_r2l8">krankheıt <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> ſeins leıbs 
<add><ab facs="#facs_305_r1l1">der er noch eins </ab><ab facs="#facs_305_r1l2">teıls an Jm hat </ab><ab facs="#facs_305_r1l3">als wır <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nemen</expan> </ab></add> / demſelben dıenſt niht mer vor mocht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_305_r2l9">geſein vnd <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> niht <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> von Jm denn <expan>fröm<ex>m</ex>keıt</expan> vnd guts </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_305_r2l10"><expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> <expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> wır eẅch mıt fleıſſ Jr wellet Jm vmb <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wıllen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_305_r2l11">guten <expan>wılle<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>beweıſ<ex>en</ex></expan> . vnd gütlıch ledıg <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd <expan>ſchaff<ex>en</ex></expan> als wır </ab>
